room_title: Escape room "The Tomb of Atahualpa" by Enigma Escape Experience in Salem
room_description: Your archaeologist friend is in trouble once again - this time in South America, near Cuzco, Peru. Excavations here have brought him in contact with a local tribe who claim to be the descendants of the last Incan Emperor, Atahualpa. But they also protect a mysterious tomb that could change the record of Incan history. Your friend may have underestimated the lengths the "Descendants" will go to protect the tomb and its secrets.
